data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome home! Beautiful Ranch Style 2 bedrooms, 2 baths home in desirable Lake Bosse Oaks Community. Foyer leads to large living room with high ceilings and wood burning fireplace. Spacious dining room with sliders to the back porch and kitchen with a good size pantry. All appliances are included. Very Split bedroom plan which could allow for two master bedrooms. Inside laundry room with lots of storage and exterior door. Master bedroom boasts a huge walk-in closet and master bath has double sinks and separate shower and tub. This bathroom has also access to a beautiful and covered back porch which is large enough for entertaining or just relaxing overlooks over-sized back yard with bonus 1/4 acre past the fence which is county maintained. Total property size is .6 acres. There is a good size shed for extra storage. The side entry an oversized two (2) car garage with plenty of room for two full size vehicles and different tools. As one of its upgrades, this property is protected by a security camera system inside and outside. You’ll love the neighborhood! It has access to Lake Bosse which allows small boats, kayaks, and paddle boards. This friendly community is located near shops, restaurants, has easy access to 1-4 and 414 as is also closed to Maitland and Altamonte Springs. Don’t miss your chance at this property. BRING YOUR BEST OFFER TODAY!
